In this first practice section, you will hear a sequence of syllables with different pitches, a pause, then another sequence with different pitches.

Your task is to determine whether the syllables in the first sequence are in the same or different order than the syllables in the second sequence.

To continue with the study, you must get 7/12 trials correct on the next 12 trials.

In this first practice section, you will hear a sequence of syllables with different pitches, a pause, then another sequence with different pitches.

Your task is to determine whether the PITCHes in the first sequence are in the same or different order than the PITCHes in the second sequence.
